pull_request.title: Task interactivity
pull_request.body:
- Add new module JavaScript files `clearCompleted.js` and `filtered.js` and imported them.
- Contain functions that react appropriately to the status updates (completed: true/false) when triggered.
- Existing event listener to the checkbox `(change)`
- Update items object's value for completed key upon user actions.
- Implement a function for the "Clear all completed" button with `filter() method`
- Store the updated array of items in local storage, so the user gets the correct list of values after the page reloads therefore any changes made to the list are preserved.
